{"tid":2308824,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府擬明年7月向輪候公屋逾3年住戶發放現金津貼，1人住戶每月可獲1250元","createTime":"2020-12-02T07:14:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T16:45:13.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"63a317a2ee9f44f35d3a97ed737dcc45ab8a694b","tid":2308824,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:14:22.000Z","msg":"政府計劃由明年7月起，向輪候公屋超過3年的住戶發放現金津貼，1人住戶每月可獲1250元，資助額最高的6人或以上輪候住戶每月可獲3850元。<br />\n<br />\n運輸及房屋局向立法會提交文件，表示申請人本身要輪候公屋超過3年、沒有家庭成員居於公營房屋、沒有領取綜援及未獲首次公屋編配等。<br />\n<br />\n計劃將會試行3年，涉及約80多億元開支，估計明年中推行時，將有約9萬個住戶可能合乎資格申請現金津貼。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563175-20201202.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563175-20201202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=TN93oS71akEChVkkxtef2RZZVu6JdVYNpUv5YkkCXtQ%3D&h=0ca3528e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1563175-20201202.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e6a2250f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1563175-20201202.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"f860924187137ea89f92a12bb6a978501615ca71","tid":2308824,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"派千二黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbe3894494a9b8c2969f1ac6422b2a050bd6594c","tid":2308824,"uid":13395,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f860924187137ea89f92a12bb6a978501615ca71","tid":2308824,"uid":68689,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:18:59.000Z","msg":"派千二黎把撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:19:33.000Z","msg":"好過冇啦"},{"pid":"80440e2953c0b137c3fabc62b14c91d79c1c15d7","tid":2308824,"uid":5654,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T07:20:00.000Z"